message:
I want to make sure that we are specifically talking about MC Phil in a situation.

Situation: he's in a crap job that makes him bitter. (Other people have similar jobs, but don't get bitter about it.) I see this replaying every morning when he wakes up: the Dylan song says, "You're still stuck here," and then he must go do a report that he hates. {Plus, we've already said that the solution to this is "being wanted."}

I'm not sure exactly when this guy transitions to the OS Reporter. I see a lot of what he does with the rest of his day as fall-out from trying to bed Rita.
